==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: news-letter
<hw>news"-let`ter</hw></mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <def>A circular letter, written or printed for the purpose
of disseminating news. This was the name given to the earliest English
newspapers.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> newssheet.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Newsman</ent>⟦br⟧
